U.S. crypto exchange app traffic remains a reliable gauge of retail momentum. The market’s trending higher, and last week’s jump to 1.2M daily active users is encouraging — but we likely need to clear 1.5M DAUs for true liftoff. A major catalyst — like the surge after Trump’s election — could quickly ignite a fresh retail wave. Until then, interest remains muted (still well below November levels), and betting on a full-blown alt season looks risky.
